---
// FullBleed — breaks its content out of the PageWrapper padding and any
// Container so it spans the full viewport width. For edge-to-edge hero
// imagery. Use sparingly — most content should stay within <Container>.
// The breakout math assumes a horizontally-centered containing block,
// which holds under the standard PageWrapper + centered Container shell.
---

<div class="full-bleed">
    <slot />
</div>
